Obviously, Q contains the historical global best solution g ‚àó for the whole population and all
individual best solutions gi (1 ‚â§ i ‚â§ n) in history. In addition, the global best solution of the
whole population is the best among all gi , so that f (g ‚àó ) = min(f (gi )), 1 ‚â§ i ‚â§ n.

